{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_46","type":"agent_message","text":"# Review: APPROVED\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Checklist\n- [x] Daemon task and worktree lease domain models are implemented with the required states/fields and persisted under `.ralph-burning/daemon/tasks/*.json` and `.ralph-burning/daemon/leases/*.json`.\n- [x] Routing resolution matches the spec: command overrides labels, labels override workspace default, built-in presets are validated strictly, malformed `rb:flow:*` labels warn, and conflicting labels fail explicitly.\n- [x] Task creation/claiming enforces the core invariants: duplicate active issue tasks are rejected, one writer lock per project is enforced, one lease per task is enforced, and claim creates deterministic worktrees plus durable lease state.\n- [x] Daemon execution covers the required lifecycle: one task per poll cycle, rebase before dispatch, project creation/resume integration, active-task heartbeats, failure-class handling, terminal cleanup, abort, retry, and reconcile flows.\n- [x] Daemon journal events, unit coverage, conformance feature coverage, CLI regression coverage, and full-suite verification are present and consistent with the slice’s acceptance criteria.\n\n## Notes\nEvidence is present in the implementation:\n- Models and ports: [model.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/model.rs#L10), [mod.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/mod.rs#L23), [fs.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/fs.rs#L921)\n- Routing and invariants: [routing.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/routing.rs#L13), [task_service.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/task_service.rs#L33), [lease_service.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/lease_service.rs#L23)\n- Loop/CLI behavior, including the prior review fixes: [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs#L109), [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs#L180), [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs#L462), [daemon.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs#L132), [worktree.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/worktree.rs#L71)\n- Coverage: [automation_runtime_test.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/automation_runtime_test.rs#L38), [cli.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/cli.rs#L385), [daemon_routing.feature](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/daemon_routing.feature#L1), [daemon_lifecycle.feature](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/daemon_lifecycle.feature#L1)\n\nVerification also checked out: `nix develop -c cargo test` passed locally with `82` CLI tests and `312` unit tests.\n\n## Commit Message\ndaemon: approve routing, lease, and lifecycle implementation after review-response fixes"}}
